title: Coming Soon!! Northern Pines Apartments Huge Upgraded 2 bedroom 2 bath
posting_body: ['COMING SOON!!!', 'Beautiful Northern Pines Apartments two bedroom two full bath apartments homes.', 'Possibly as early as October!', 'Here at Northern Pines, our two bedroom offers:', 'Over 1100 Square Feet!', 'Oversized Walk In Closets in both bedrooms!', '*Minutes from I-285 Church Street Exit', '*Picnic Area', '*BBQ grilling area', '*Patios and balconies', '*Open Floor plan', '*Beautifully landscaped', '*Total Electric', '*cable ready', '*updated flooring', '*online rental payments', '*24 Hour Emergency Maintenance and much more.', 'We are minutes from major eateries, Northlake Mall, banking and the beautiful Stone Mountain Park close by.', 'Our hours of operation are Mondays/Weds/Fridays of each', 'Northern Pines carry’s two bedrooms only.', '774 Northern Ave.', 'Clarkston, GA 30021', 'show contact info', 'Prices start as low as $1,250 (includes water)', 'We perform Criminal, Credit, Rental and employment background checks', 'Application Fee is just $50.00 with a $150.00 reservation fee', 'Equal Housing opportunity', 'Prices are subject to change', '774 Northern Ave.']
